title: Forklifter 2014  - Warehouse and Logistics Simulator - HI2U
description:
HI2U!
 
Forklifter 2014 (c) UIG Entertainment
 
Release Date : 3rd of March, 2014
Protection   : -
Type         : Simulator
Size         : 34 x 15mb
 
Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~
 
Are you ready for your new challenge? Get ready to take over the 
control of your original "Jungheinrich" Forklift! Just the best 
drivers will level up in the Highscore list. The fastest drivers 
will receive a special bonus. 

Enjoy the game in full 3D and feel the realistic driving 
experience. Varied scenarios like the warehouse, construction 
zone or port zone guarantee variety.

Note:
~~~~~
The game is also known as Warehouse & Logistics Simulator.
  
Install:
~~~~~~~
  
Unrar, mount/burn, install the game and play.
